universum.studios.android.intent

Class DialerIntent

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.intent.BaseIntent<DialerIntent>
      • universum.studios.android.intent.DialerIntent

  • public class DialerIntent
extends BaseIntent<DialerIntent>
    A BaseIntent builder implementation providing API for building and starting of intents targeting a dialer related applications.

    This intent builder requires only a phone number to be specified via phoneNumber(String).

    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
    See Also:
    SmsIntent

      • ensureCanBuildOrThrow

        protected void ensureCanBuildOrThrow()
        Description copied from class: BaseIntent
        Called to ensure that this builder can build its Intent from its current data.

        If there are some required data missing/not specified, an exception indicating such state should be thrown. The default exception may be created via BaseIntent.cannotBuildIntentException(String).

        Overrides:
